OL,3,C'Millions of people have bought a lie'
OL,4,Cover arena attack, court told
OL,6,FTaking to the stand on the third day
OL,7,Fof a civil harassment trial, Mr Hall
OL,8,Ftold the court in London he believed
OL,9,Fthat no one was "genuinely injured" in
OL,10,Fthe attack, with evidence showing the
OL,11,Fincident was "faked".
OL,13,FMartin Hibbert, and his daughter Eve,
OL,14,Fbrought legal action for harassment
OL,15,Fand data protection against Mr Hall
OL,16,Fover several videos and a book where
OL,17,Fhe claims the bombing was a "hoax", as
OL,18,Fwell as "secretly filming" Miss
OL,19,FHibbert and her mother at their house.
