OL,6,FSalman Abedi killed 22 people and
OL,7,Finjured hundreds when he detonated the
OL,8,Fhomemade rucksack-bomb in the crowd of
OL,9,Fconcert-goers, with the Hibberts some
OL,10,Fof the nearest people to him at the
OL,11,Ftime of the blast.
OL,13,FAbedi's brother, Hashem Abedi, was
OL,14,Fjailed for life in August 2020 after
OL,15,Fhe was convicted of assisting the
OL,16,Fterror plot.
OL,18,FThe public inquiry into the atrocity
OL,19,Fbegan on September 7 2020 and ended on
OL,20,FFebruary 15 2022.
