OL,6,FIn its third report, published in
OL,7,FMarch 2023, inquiry chairman Sir John
OL,8,FSaunders concluded the attack might
OL,9,Fhave been prevented if MI5 had acted
OL,10,Fon key intelligence received in the
OL,11,Fmonths prior.
OL,13,FJonathan Price, for the Hibberts,
OL,14,Fasked Mr Hall why he would not "just
OL,15,Fbelieve" the pair and Miss Hibbert's
OL,16,Fmother Sarah Gillbard about the
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,19,FMr Hall replied: "Because there is no
OL,20,Fevidence to show any of their claims."
